and Redux.

Make sure to keep the state management strategy simple, especially for small
apps. Over-engineering can add unnecessary complexity.


ADVANCED METHODS

USING NAVIGATOR.OF(CONTEXT).PUSH

 * Send data back from received screen:

class SendingScreen extends StatelessWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return ElevatedButton(
